<h1>Frequently Asked Questioned</h1>
<h2>What should I wear?</h2>

The ceremony is "festive attire" or "dressy casual". For the guys we recommend dress slacks and a sports coat or blazer. A tie isn't necessary but if you have one to show off feel free. For the ladies we recommend cocktail dresses or a dressy skirt and blouse.

October weather in Virginia can go from one extreme to the next in minutes. The ceremony and reception will both be held outside so make sure you dress for the weather. 





